        <body>
            <p>
                <addressee>Rev I Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Dear Friend</p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">I intended to have written<lb/> you a long letter but I am suffering
                very<lb/> much from a <hi rend="underline">Boil</hi> on my Back the pain<lb/> is so
                intense that I have had no rest for nearly<lb/> a week and it seems at this moment
                no better.<lb/> I wrote you therefore <hi rend="underline">standing</hi>, as I can
                not <hi rend="underline">sit</hi> down<lb/> for the following order</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">3 Setts Prayer Books in paper @/12<lb/> each and One Daily prayer
                bound cheap<lb/> edition—the setts Books are for <persName>Mr Ben<lb/>
                    Mordecai</persName>, who will pay for them on receipt<lb/> of Bill &amp;c all
                the family are well and<lb/>
                <del>have</del>
                <add>?</add>. I trust you are well<lb/> give my kind regards to
                    <persName>Solomon</persName> &amp; family<lb/>__The Occident is here__I
                    <sic>dont</sic> think<lb/> you will be troubled with “O” any more.<lb/> I must
                conclude as I am in<lb/> great pain yours Truly &amp; Sincerely</p>
            <p rend="indent(8)">
                <persName role="author">S. N. Carralby</persName>
            </p>
            <p>
                <date>Wednesday Oct 15 1851</date>
            </p>
            <p>
                <placeName>Charleston</placeName>
            </p>
            <pb n="2V"/>
            <p rend="indent(5)">Recd. <date>Oct. 20<hi rend="sup">th</hi></date>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">
                <addressee>Rev I Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">Editor of Occident</p>
            <p rend="indent(6)"><placeName>Walnut Street</placeName> near</p>
            <p rend="indent(7)">
                <placeName>the tenth</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(6)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
        </body>
